Dear <%= @membership.user.first_name %>,

This notice is to inform you that you have been assigned a membership in <%= @membership.description %>, for a term starting on <%= @membership.starts_at.to_s :long_ordinal %> and ending on <%= @membership.ends_at.to_s :long_ordinal %>.

<% if @membership.position.authority.join_message -%>
<%= @membership.position.authority.join_message %>

<% end -%>
<% if @membership.position.join_message -%>
<%= @membership.position.join_message %>

<% end -%>
